Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:36.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's turned into a slum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:40.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But it looks like there are still\Npeople in the apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you live in an apartment, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:48.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who knows? The address looks like\Na freestanding house... Yeah, as if!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:58.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(315,162)}Episode 3:\NOn the night of the Late Show
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:14.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ground zero of the blast is that way,\Nso your place should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:19.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But you know, those buildings\Ndon't look like people live in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's at least go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:38.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're... sure you've got the right place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:40.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's the right address.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There should be a power source somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:06.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But would a person normally\Nlive in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it remind you of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You found the key without thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:15.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Mmm, I've got a sort of feel for it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:20.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:49.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, little guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:59.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This must be where you live. I mean,\Nit looks like he really knows you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:03.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's true, he does seem to know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:24.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask such a big favor.\NI know it's out of your jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then sorry, but would you wait an hour for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:33.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If I'm not back by then you can just go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:40.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Does that kid really live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:46.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The log does say he bought this whole place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one who\Nwants to erase your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You better be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Looks like we can go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You live in a shopping mall! Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:10.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But seriously, living in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:13.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's like something out of Dawn of the Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is that a movie, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure we'll find out\Nsomething if we investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The newspaper was being\Ndelivered and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:29.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There should be mail, and the\Nregistration for this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(229,239)\i1\fs45\fnSegoe Print}I'll kill you for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs45\fnSegoe Print\pos(399,272)}Takizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:53.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,For real? This is where that photo was taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It looks like this is where Akira Takizawa lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:00.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but what the hell was I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:06.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa! What's wrong?\NDid you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's a movie theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What, did you want to invite us to a late show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is that where you live, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is a pretty nice apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This has to be your home, Takizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:09.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be. Look, you remembered\Nall about those movies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:14.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That must be because you were\Nthe manager here or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Manager, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You can see ground zero from here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:44.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Are there any movies you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Request any one you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I can play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about movies,\Nsince I don't watch many of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You can think of at least one, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Like the one you saw on your\Nfirst date, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:06.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, well, then... That French movie\Nwith the dolphin and the diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:13.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Even though you don't remember\Na thing about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Too true. But why that movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:24.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Because the person I always\Nloved liked that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:39.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Juiz, I need a favor. There's\Na movie I want to see right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:43.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm in the movie\Ntheater in Toyosu right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:50.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll look into the\Nmovies sent to that theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Please wait a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:57.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Noblesse oblige. I pray you'll\Nbe a savior tonight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:01.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Dunno about that, but I'd\Nat least like to be a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:11.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this place, a refugee camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And this mountain of cell phones...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:26.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I get it, so that kid is involved\Nin the NEET disappearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:31.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So a Selecao was behind the\Nmissile attack and that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:36.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'd've scored a serious coup if I'd\Nactually checked activity histories
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:39.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,instead of just using the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:43.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm getting myself a new\Neight billion and doing life over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:46.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,so it's got nothing to do with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:55.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Gotta turn my cell phone\Noff before the movie starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:10:03.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The number you're calling is\Neither out of range or powered off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:09.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I do have to take my hat off\Nto Osugi's effort, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think his struggles are futile, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(357,301)\fnComic Sans MS}Tell everyone I\Nstayed at your\Nplace tonight!\NPlease! That's\Nwhat I told\NAsako.\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Tell everyone I stayed at your place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:21.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Please. That's what I told Asako."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, when did you get this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess around eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:35.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We're going home, Osugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she's really staying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(449,239)}The Cold Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:47.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was the projectionist here\Nafter all, like in Cinema Paradiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:54.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a huge screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.35,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:09.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:27.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Here by yourself, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:31.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then you're not here to arrest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:33.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You noticed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So you came for a personal visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:45.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, but... This thing sure saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:50.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see, so you checked into my log?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:54.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,By log, do you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:12:00.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Also, what's Selecao?\NSee, the thing is, I have amnesia,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and I don't remember anything about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:07.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So there's a lot of things I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did you really erase your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:24.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see. So Harima Neuroscience\NInstitute's brainwashing program
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,really can erase memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll use it myself sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:33.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But first, I need to get that phone from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:43.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You were careless, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:13:00.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What is that phone? How much was on yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You're sure persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the money left on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:18.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'd guess you started out\Nwith ten billion, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:22.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But there's no way anyone could\Nsave this rotten-to-the-core country
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,with a measly ten billion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How dare they pull me into\Nthis stupid "obligation"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Detectives sure are strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:39.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Mister... that girl has nothing... to do with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:45.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Killing people costs money.\NI'm not going to do anything wasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:52.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I'll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,When the money on a Noblesse phone runs out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:59.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,someone called the Supporter\Napparently comes to kill its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:06.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Too bad, kid. That girl may live,\Nbut you're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:21.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This makes us even, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:25.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's a Supporter? Yet another mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:33.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry... It doesn't look like I'm\Ngoing to make the late show...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:03.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Do you know where Takizawa went?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If he didn't want to be with me,\Nhe could've just said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Nice message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\fnCentury\i1}You Jerk!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, shall we go return this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:05.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"I got money for us to fool around for life on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:12.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I called for a car, so meet me in Kabukicho."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(241,150)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(254,235)}[Arrange for\Nan ato taxi]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(261,284)}[Kill the three men\Nin front of him]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(277,321)}[Social expenses]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've used it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:28.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's the same model, so it\Nshould work the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Dammit. Guess I'll ask Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There's something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What would happen if someone\Nelse got their hands on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Could anyone use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:48.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It employs fingerprint recognition,\Nso no one else would be able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:56.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No, that makes things safe.\NI see. Talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:09.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Dammit, why do I always\Nscrew things up like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308,231)}Public Phone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(252,309)}Saki
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242,363)}Me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:27.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:34.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Come on, Detective Kondou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:42.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And here I am trying to return\Nyour precious ID to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,At least answer the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:55.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In the middle of Kabukicho.\NGet your ass over here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:59.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Kabukicho... So, how do I get there, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Are you yanking my chain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:05.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I told you, I have no memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:10.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, go toward Kiba and take\Nthe Metropolitan Expressway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:10.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(291,209)}Kabukicho First Street
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Misae...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:35.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's this "money for us\Nto fool around for life on"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:42.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you wrote a text to\Nyour lover and then sent it to your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:52.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This ends it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Shut up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll call you an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:32.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't poke your nose in.\NIt looks like this is the end for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:36.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't just up and die! I still\Nhave things I want to ask--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:45.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There should be ten other Selecao\Nbesides us with the same phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:52.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The Selecao are players forced\Nto participate in this damn game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:55.56,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Purchase logs go to your phone, too, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:20:00.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Use those to find other Selecao\Nand ask them about the rest of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ask them, "Who am I?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:06.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That is, assuming there's anyone willing to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,a dangerous Selecao like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A dangerous Selecao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:18.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You gathered 20,000 NEETs at ground\Nzero and tried to kill them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:25.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, or are you the Supporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So that's it. That's why Misae...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I have no clue what you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:34.76,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You got me. Take this and get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:58.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, I was trying\Nto carry out justice, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night is a seal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future